## Instructor Guide

### Pre-Class Preparation

- [ ] Print Support Cheat Sheet, Reflection, Intent, and Buddy cards
- [ ] Open community "Hello Post" thread
- [ ] Test phone-in line for office hours
- [ ] Prepare large-print PDFs for download
- [ ] Set up quiz automation (tags: `quiz3_ready_to_launch`, `quiz3_cautious_capable`, `quiz3_preparing_to_begin`)

### Timing Guide

- **L0.1:** 20 minutes (Welcome, Support, Tech-Light Promise)
- **L0.2:** 20 minutes (Course Tour, Community)
- **L0.3:** 30 minutes (Readiness Quiz, Outcomes, Next Steps)
- **L0.4:** 20 minutes (Reflection, Intent, Commitment)
- **Total:** ~90 minutes (can be split across multiple sessions)

### Common Questions & Responses

**"I'm not techy."**
→ "You only need three clicks today; we'll do them together. If it breaks, we fix it. Everything is printable, and you can call us anytime."

**"I'm busy."**
→ "Two hours blocked beats 'someday'—and it compounds. The hour-a-day rhythm is designed to fit real life. You can always do the Essentials track if time is tight."

**"What if I'm not cut out for this?"**
→ "That's what the quiz clarifies. All outcomes include a next step. There's no 'wrong' answer—just different starting points. We're here to help you grow into this."

**"I don't have a business idea yet."**
→ "Perfect! Download the 10 Business Ideas Guide. Many retirees discover ideas they hadn't considered. Module 1 will help you explore your skills and passions."

### Accessibility Notes

- Always offer "read aloud" option
- Provide large-print PDFs (16-18pt)
- Phone alternatives for all digital activities
- Keyboard navigation works on all pages
- Captions on all videos
- Transcripts available for download

### Low-Tech Pairing

If someone won't use the forum:

- Pair phone-to-phone
- Provide phone number exchange option
- Schedule weekly phone check-ins instead of forum posts

### Email Automation

After L0.3 (Quiz completion):

- Trigger outcome-specific Email #1 from quiz pack
- Tag contact in CRM: `quiz3_ready_to_launch`, `quiz3_cautious_capable`, or `quiz3_preparing_to_begin`
- Include link to appropriate 5-Day Starter Plan day

### Good/Better/Best Exemplars

**Intent Statement:**

- _Good:_ "Sell crafts locally."
- _Better:_ "Sell five knitted scarves in December."
- _Best:_ "Pre-sell 5 scarves @ $25 each by Dec 10 via church bulletin."

### Escalation Path

1. **Tech Issue:** Check Troubleshooting Matrix → Email support → Phone support
2. **Content Question:** Forum post → Office hours → 1:1 call
3. **Accountability:** Buddy check-in → Community post → Office hours

