## 7-Step Validation Checklist

- [x] **Outcome & Scope:** Observable outcomes (MO1, MO2, MO3) with matching activities
- [x] **Accuracy & Specificity:** Concrete support options, clear quiz outcomes, specific next steps
- [x] **Accessibility:** Large-print PDFs, keyboard navigation, phone options, captions
- [x] **Structure:** Proper module tag, cross-links to Module 1, file paths correct
- [x] **Consistency:** Tone matches course brand, no AI references, age-positive language
- [x] **Hooks & Funnel:** Lead magnets integrated, quiz outcomes route to 5-Day Plan, email automation ready
- [x] **Export & Ops:** Workbook printable, quiz functional, email sequences ready, support channels published

